<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <!-- Bootstrap (CSS, JS) -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-KyZXEAg3QhqLMpG8r+8fhAXLRk2vvoC2f3B09zVXn8CA5QIVfZOJ3BCsw2P0p/We"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-U1DAWAznBHeqEIlVSCgzq+c9gqGAJn5c/t99JyeKa9xxaYpSvHU5awsuZVVFIhvj"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>

    <!-- Web Font -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Black+Han+Sans&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

    <title>회원가입</title>

    <style>
      html,
      body {
        height: 100vh;
        background-color: white;
      }

      #container {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100vh;
      }

      #site_name {
        font-family: "Black Han Sans", sans-serif;
      }
      #site_name:hover {
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 2px #f2df80;
      }

      a:link {
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      a:visited,
      a:hover {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: black;
      }

      .signup_box {
        min-width: 30vw;
        min-height: 90vh;
        padding: 10vh 0;
        box-shadow: 5px 5px 5px 5px rgba(0, 0, 255, 0.2);      
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="container" class="d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
      <div class="signup_box bg-white my-5 px-5 rounded">
        <div>
          <span><%=id%></span>님 회원가입 축하드립니다!<br>
          <span><%=name%></span><br>
          <span><%=email%></span><br>
          <span><%=gender%></span><br>
        </div>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center py-2">
          <span>이미 계정이 있으신가요? &nbsp</span>
          <a href="http://101.101.218.8:8000/login">로그인하러 가기</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>